Package chromatynk.chromatynk_g6.LYnk

Class LYnkBaseListener

java.lang.Object
chromatynk.chromatynk_g6.LYnk.LYnkBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
LYnkListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class LYnkBaseListener extends Object implements LYnkListener
This class provides an empty implementation of LYnkListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
